{"tid":1044432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"妹子倒立失敗下體微露…竟遭愛犬硬騎上演「老狗推車」","createTime":"2019-03-03T01:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T11:11:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5492ed2681accb981a9a2e2aa6f2b09885eed5","tid":1044432,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T01:26:43.000Z","msg":"許多民眾做運動時，都會讓毛小孩在一旁陪著，然而日前在歐美及大陸網站上，瘋傳了一段逗趣影像，一名女子在戶外嘗試倒立，沒想到不小心失敗跌倒，結果一旁狗狗的自然反應，讓網友們全都傻眼！<br />\n <br />\n當時這名女子在戶外做瑜珈運動，只見她正嘗試挑戰一個倒立的動作，失敗倒地踉蹌的疊出一個「下體外露」的尷尬姿勢，結果原本在一旁玩耍的狗狗，一見到此情此景，竟然情不自禁的上前「硬騎」女主人，直接上演一段老狗推車的畫面，但隨著女子起身拍拍屁股，狗狗也沒有進一步的動作。<br />\n <br />\n這一段尷尬畫面不僅在歐美網路上瘋傳，就連大陸社群也做成GIF檔，許多網友笑稱「這真是最糗的裝逼失敗」、「這狗的命也太好了」、「跟主人感情真好」、「牠應該準備很久了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/092548_985f3b36e296983bb8f3114103210fa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F092548_985f3b36e296983bb8f3114103210fa5.png&h=9c1ce925&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/092550_69d6231dc4b06d992da5d820995a2ea2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F092550_69d6231dc4b06d992da5d820995a2ea2.png&h=2d8748c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/092551_290cc5e15d8344fb74dc17c657ab9c47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F092551_290cc5e15d8344fb74dc17c657ab9c47.png&h=962ad5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/092552_6b3e9ef8315f3fb999e7c2918e77ddaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F092552_6b3e9ef8315f3fb999e7c2918e77ddaf.png&h=525b19d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gfycat.com/clutteredflimsychick\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgfycat.com%2Fcl